text:
Update of the Gnotepad+ (editors/gnotepad+) to the new 1.2.1 version.

Following fixes and enhancements are provided:

+ Port now uses gnomelibs instead of plain GTK;
+ port's documentation distributed in separate distfile now being installed, if
  NOPORTDOCS has not been set;
+ USE_X_PREFIX added to Makefile, because obviously this port falls into the X11 category;
+ libintl dependency added to port's Makefile;
+ WWW added to the pkg/DESCR;
+ MASTER_SITES updated to reflect reality;
+ pkg/PLIST has been sorted;
+ "Date created:" slightly adjusted to match commonly accepted conventions.
